// Property Pulse daily board — data layer.
// Reads the lane snapshots generated by pulse_*_metrics.py (real AppFolio /
// Property Meld reads + renewals tracker) plus the entity registry
// (entities.json) that powers the entity-slice layer (master plan §6).
//
// Phase D contract: each lane snapshot MAY carry an optional `records` array
// of per-row facts alongside the `live` aggregate block. When records are
// present the board recomputes every displayed number through
// pulse-aggregate.ts (§6.4 honesty invariant); when absent it falls back to
// the generator's `live` block and entity scoping is unavailable.
import fs from 'fs';
import path from 'path';

